t is the same. I also tried the following solution proposed on a forum: "replace json by jsonp". By doing that, the results are displayed in the console, thanks to <code>console.log(result)</code>, but the loop <code>each</code> is not ok and the error 'ajax request failed' appears </p>  <p>I do not know how to solve the problem, can anyone help me to solve it?</p>